name: Lost in the dust
description:
from the collection "Inside songs" 

The one you wanted got lost in the dust
He turned into a bird and got lost behind the fence
He wrote your name on the wings of birds
He wrote on the green trunk of the trees
He told her one day when it was raining
Another day he wrote on the sea wave
The sea swept him away with its waves
The bird got lost and made him cry
The one you wanted got lost in the dust
He turned into a bird and got lost behind the fence

The wind blew and he walked in the woods
He crossed out your name from everywhere
See what the separation brought him
What did you write for him?
The one you wanted got lost in the dust
He turned into a bird and got lost behind the fence

Behrooz Razavi
